info.description: Place out your tribespeople to explore the islands of the marshland, collect resources, and get in the way of your opponents.
info.helpText:
Begin by clicking the 3P setup or 4P setup button for a 3 or 4 player game.

Click "Spread Goodies" to randomly distribute the resources on the board. After finishing the first phase of the game, track points in the top score tracker for each player. Then click the "Recall People", "Recall Goodies", and "Spread Goodies" buttons to reset the resources and tribespeople, while leaving the huts on the boards. Score the second phase in the second point tracker.
